{"tid":897004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載]睇高登連登仔講女人，真係連自己都覺得自己on9","createTime":"2018-11-10T14:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T22:16:15.000Z","uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51928ee6d88c9269dd4114fc496e812f87cf54d0","tid":897004,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"有曰「癲佬有傻根，癡漢在雙登」，每次我不小心看到有人分享高登連登仔講兩性關係和相處，我就情不自禁浮出一句歇後語：<span style=\"color: red;\">太監騎馬</span>，誰想在這種仍靠<span style=\"color: red;\">過時介面維生的濕鳩論壇搏出位</span>，就靠語不驚人死不休，閣下唔知就嚇死，知就笑死。<br />\n<br />\n例如附圖，如果閣下靠這種「意見」去識女仔，真箇屎都冇得你食&mdash;&mdash;普遍香港女人真的這副德性嗎？可能我圈子淺窄吧，會有這種思（妄）想的人一般都不是各位正常社交會遇到的人，反而比較像窩在雙登論壇九噏當祕笈的人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「工具人」「吊高來賣」「港女愛MK」「愛中出即飛」「港女語錄」⋯⋯如此短短一百幾十字已經一堆帽子亂扣，滑坡滑坡再滑坡的定律，跟細路仔唔聽媽媽話然後第二朝死咗差無九幾，世上竟然會有女人「愛（被）中出即飛」，簡直是N不思議大發現，原來香港女人竟然以生仔唔知誰是老豆為榮，當真莫名其妙的偏見VSOP。會說這種話的人，仇雌恨女到極，路人甲驟眼睇此人之言，或許以為那人受了超重擊情傷，因愛成恨然後在網上以無責任批鬥女人而自豪。<br />\n</span><br />\n這種視「港女」為讎的言論，早就超越以偏概全，簡直是單靠蘋果動新聞了解女人的水平，躲在網絡世界去了解人性的人，長篇大論，原來自己從未碰過女人，自卑復自大，才會如此大言不慚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一段人際關係觸礁，真的只是一句「港女愛MK」解釋得了嗎？<span style=\"color: red;\">在下能想像到假如我只是一名尋常女子，假如有（不）幸地認識到如此思路的雙登仔，趨吉避凶遠離癲佬保平安乃動物本能，</span>這是因果，閣下帶着幾副有色眼鏡去誤判女人，未出發先興奮，繼而網上圍爐取暖當開心大發現，教人如何不視你如云根呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曾經人才輩出的雙登論壇，現在一大票如此水平之流發噏風，學江澤民.jpg 話齋：執柒咗佢啦，咪鬼累人累物，或許網友瀏覽雙登網站前，必須奉政府諭：未成年或心智未成熟請馬上離開， thank you for your co-operation。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2018/11/10/187030/%E7%9D%87%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E8%AC%9B%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E9%80%A3%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1on9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F187030%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%258C%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%2580%25A3%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%25BE%2597%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1on9&d=5r1S28h%2BdlPdArFxc0HKil0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=95de3106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2018/11/10/187030/%E7%9D%87%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E8%AC%9B%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E9%80%A3%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1on9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326326ddcb98fa5a453d3aaba6a97489f89c5d99","tid":897004,"uid":55924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"到底咩人會咁激動?"},{"pid":"54840e0f083a7c41566db51b6a944b4be861e1b8","tid":897004,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"曾經人才輩出的<span style=\"color: red;\">雙</span>登論壇<br />\n<br />\n呢度有咩人才？<br />\n<br />\n偷人野嘅連尼住？<br />\n定捉人錯字嘅肥絲（都係連尼住）？"},{"pid":"da783636c92c599713532a6d6279353e888fdad4","tid":897004,"uid":143288,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"打一大篇文講啲阿媽係女人嘅道理仲一副看透世事的樣 我都係睇到都覺得on9"},{"pid":"0cacf29369ea930bd224ba7d11af2727fec33649","tid":897004,"uid":28195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"輔仁媒體就算鳩數喇，有撚人睇咩"},{"pid":"c94da813dc63bfb58cecf137f2b08260b4e1ee59","tid":897004,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"下十年前,高登已經係咁架啦喎,佢有冇上高高登架以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f403eb637af7bf05a797af18b8cecd4a8309435","tid":897004,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4786de53f40394537bd36429c776090dc95156c","tid":897004,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:14:53.000Z","msg":"拉～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83d95ec07387e08fb571619b97e1fd46b3eb742","tid":897004,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56a02e51e5e9dcb46811a7157854267d9e3e737","tid":897004,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T21:58:41.000Z","msg":"搏出位個下笑咗<br />\n唔知邊個搏邊個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05628b78463e58bb5abb608b7b7f2500a09241e","tid":897004,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T22:16:15.000Z","msg":"同連登班社交障礙兒童認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}